<bibRefCitation author="Namiki, C. &amp; Bonecker, A. C. T. &amp; Castro, M. S." box="[899,1143,312,338]" pageId="7" pageNumber="48" pagination="292 - 295" refId="ref17371" refString="Namiki, C., Bonecker, A. C. T. &amp; Castro, M. S. (2007) Carapidae larvae (Acanthomorpha, Paracanthopterygii, Ophidiiformes) from the oceanic region of the southwest Atlantic Ocean off Brazil (12 - 22 ° S). Deep-sea Research I, 54, 292 - 295." type="journal article" year="2007">
Namiki 
<emphasis box="[995,1046,312,337]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="48">et al</emphasis>
